branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
13-MXS clean room air slide tables, rated for contamination grade 3, are great for applications that call for precise movement ranging from 10-150mm typically requiring a cylinder and precision guide. The MXS is available in 6 bore sizes, each with set stroke lengths and is standard with auto-switch capability.
&lt;/p&gt;

